Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「君が許さなかった世界はこんなにも綺麗だ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:40.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「悲しみを生むこと、全てが悪だとでも言うのか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現実の銃口　突きつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矜持たちが　壊れても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僕は僕でしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:55.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Against the gunpoint, ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'll rise like the break dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I save them for the final day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dream of the world for me and "fantasia"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's time to go...Unshaken mind!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揺れる視界を薙ぎ払い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愛すべき"正義"を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:28.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}語られない明日のために生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儚さと　痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}狂気だけが走らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全てが還る日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:41.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I face out, hold out to world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:34.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「你所不原谅的世界是这样美丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:40.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「制造悲伤的一切都是邪恶吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现实的枪口已指向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使矜持悉数破碎崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也仍然只是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:55.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迎着枪口 随时准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会像破晓的黎明那样喷薄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为末日将他们拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向往着为我与幻想而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是时候启程了…怀着坚定的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去改变世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}清空动摇的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寻找值得热爱的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:28.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为无从诉说的明天而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在虚幻与痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有疯狂在穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一切回归之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:41.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我将勇敢地面对世界
